<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><songwriters><songwriter>余慧迪</songwriter><songwriter>李茜</songwriter></songwriters></iTunesMetadata><amll:meta key="musicName" value="花焰照亮的旅途"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="FoldEcho"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="无限暖暖"/><amll:meta key="album" value="无限暖暖——花焰迎新岁"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2676045527"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="42886855"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ArSrNa"/></metadata></head><body dur="4:45.538"><div begin="14.967" end="4:45.538"><p begin="14.967" end="17.424" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.967" end="15.240">Light</span> <span begin="15.240" end="15.434">up</span> <span begin="15.434" end="15.682">the</span> <span begin="15.682" end="16.220">night</span> <span begin="16.353" end="16.707">and</span> <span begin="16.707" end="17.424">shine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">点亮夜空，闪耀光辉</span></p><p begin="17.424" end="21.542" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.424" end="17.605">So</span> <span begin="17.605" end="18.587">dazzling</span> <span begin="18.587" end="18.736">as</span> <span begin="18.736" end="20.002">dreams</span> <span begin="20.002" end="20.155">and</span> <span begin="20.155" end="21.542">desires</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如梦似愿，光芒万丈</span></p><p begin="21.779" end="24.822" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.779" end="22.011">A</span> <span begin="22.011" end="22.184">warm</span> <span begin="22.184" end="22.488">and</span> <span begin="22.488" end="23.723">glowing</span> <span begin="23.723" end="24.822">light</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">温暖柔和的光辉</span></p><p begin="25.202" end="28.121" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.202" end="25.907">Filling</span> <span begin="25.907" end="26.129">the</span> <span begin="26.129" end="26.785">whole</span> <span begin="26.785" end="28.121">sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">照亮整片天空</span></p><p begin="29.827" end="32.064" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.827" end="29.981">The</span> <span begin="29.981" end="30.280">taste</span> <span begin="30.280" end="30.466">of</span> <span begin="30.466" end="31.163">home,</span> <span begin="31.163" end="31.355">how</span> <span begin="31.355" end="32.064">sweet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像家的气息，多么甜蜜</span></p><p begin="32.064" end="36.250" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.064" end="32.261">And</span> <span begin="32.261" end="33.096">bitter</span> <span begin="33.096" end="33.239">it</span> <span begin="33.239" end="33.464">can</span> <span begin="33.464" end="34.344">be</span> <span begin="34.344" end="34.794">some</span><span begin="34.794" end="36.250">times</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有时却又那么苦涩</span></p><p begin="36.520" end="43.225" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.520" end="36.789">Guiding</span> <span begin="36.789" end="37.169">my</span> <span begin="37.169" end="37.850">heart</span> <span begin="37.850" end="38.622">e</span><span begin="38.622" end="39.236">very</span> <span begin="39.236" end="39.835">step</span> <span begin="39.835" end="40.333">through</span> <span begin="40.333" end="40.770">the</span> <span begin="40.770" end="43.225">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">指引我心，步步前行穿过黑夜</span></p><p begin="44.607" end="48.213" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.607" end="45.496">Every</span> <span begin="45.496" end="46.406">journey</span> <span begin="46.406" end="46.800">is</span> <span begin="46.800" end="47.701">unique</span> <span begin="47.701" end="48.213">just</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每段旅程都独一无二</span></p><p begin="48.213" end="51.832" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.213" end="48.642">Like</span> <span begin="48.642" end="49.121">the</span> <span begin="49.121" end="49.610">trails</span> <span begin="49.610" end="50.097">that</span> <span begin="50.097" end="50.523">fire</span><span begin="50.523" end="50.981">works</span> <span begin="50.981" end="51.400">leave</span> <span begin="51.400" end="51.832">and</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如同烟花划过的轨迹</span></p><p begin="51.832" end="55.553" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="51.832" end="52.316">Some</span> <span begin="52.316" end="52.786">will</span> <span begin="52.786" end="53.240">soar</span> <span begin="53.240" end="53.733">high,</span> <span begin="53.733" end="54.187">glow</span> <span begin="54.187" end="54.621">in</span> <span begin="54.621" end="55.061">the</span> <span begin="55.061" end="55.553">sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有的高飞，光芒闪烁</span></p><p begin="55.553" end="59.259" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.553" end="56.036">Some</span> <span begin="56.036" end="56.501">will</span> <span begin="56.501" end="56.955">wink</span> <span begin="56.955" end="57.417">out,</span> <span begin="57.417" end="57.901">sink</span> <span begin="57.901" end="58.357">in</span> <span begin="58.357" end="58.835">the</span> <span begin="58.835" end="59.259">sea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有的熄灭，沉入海底</span></p><p begin="59.259" end="1:03.015" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.259" end="59.717">I</span> <span begin="59.717" end="1:00.211">wish</span> <span begin="1:00.211" end="1:00.683">to</span> <span begin="1:00.683" end="1:01.161">shine</span> <span begin="1:01.161" end="1:02.114">brightly</span> <span begin="1:02.114" end="1:02.528">at</span> <span begin="1:02.528" end="1:03.015">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我愿夜空中璀璨闪耀</span></p><p begin="1:03.015" end="1:06.677" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.015" end="1:03.431">Yet</span> <span begin="1:03.431" end="1:03.915">fear</span> <span begin="1:03.915" end="1:04.901">being</span> <span begin="1:04.901" end="1:05.300">lost</span> <span begin="1:05.300" end="1:05.765">in</span> <span begin="1:05.765" end="1:06.232">the</span> <span begin="1:06.232" end="1:06.677">dark</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">却又惧怕迷失于黑暗</span></p><p begin="1:06.677" end="1:12.939" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.677" end="1:07.136">What</span> <span begin="1:07.136" end="1:07.613">could</span> <span begin="1:07.613" end="1:08.099">be</span> <span begin="1:08.099" end="1:08.517">more</span> <span begin="1:08.517" end="1:09.547">fleeting</span> <span begin="1:09.547" end="1:09.963">than</span> <span begin="1:09.963" end="1:10.365">this</span> <span begin="1:10.365" end="1:12.939">road?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没有什么比此路更瞬息万变</span></p><p begin="1:13.685" end="1:17.132" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:13.685" end="1:13.867">Flame</span> <span begin="1:13.867" end="1:14.115">of</span> <span begin="1:14.115" end="1:15.235">love,</span> <span begin="1:15.235" end="1:15.484">flame</span> <span begin="1:15.484" end="1:15.673">of</span> <span begin="1:15.673" end="1:17.132">life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">爱的焰火，生命之光</span></p><p begin="1:17.200" end="1:21.186" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:17.200" end="1:17.352">The</span> <span begin="1:17.352" end="1:17.769">brightest</span> <span begin="1:17.769" end="1:19.637">moment</span> <span begin="1:19.637" end="1:20.331">I</span> <span begin="1:20.331" end="1:21.186">find</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是我见过最闪亮的时光</span></p><p begin="1:21.512" end="1:24.169" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.512" end="1:22.217">May</span> <span begin="1:22.217" end="1:22.892">these</span> <span begin="1:22.892" end="1:23.612">min</span><span begin="1:23.612" end="1:24.169">utes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但愿这一刻</span></p><p begin="1:24.779" end="1:28.561" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.779" end="1:25.001">Be</span> <span begin="1:25.001" end="1:25.249">a</span> <span begin="1:25.249" end="1:25.782">new</span> <span begin="1:25.782" end="1:26.537">start</span> <span begin="1:26.537" end="1:26.723">of</span> <span begin="1:26.723" end="1:27.002">grand</span> <span begin="1:27.002" end="1:28.561">dreams</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">为盛大梦想铺开新章</span></p><p begin="1:28.561" end="1:31.604" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:28.561" end="1:28.716">Just</span> <span begin="1:28.716" end="1:28.915">keep</span> <span begin="1:28.915" end="1:30.115">going,</span> <span begin="1:30.115" end="1:30.278">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:30.278" end="1:30.481">look</span> <span begin="1:30.481" end="1:31.604">back</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">继续前行，莫回首</span></p><p begin="1:31.850" end="1:35.948" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:31.850" end="1:32.113">There</span> <span begin="1:32.113" end="1:32.329">must</span> <span begin="1:32.329" end="1:32.521">be</span> <span begin="1:32.521" end="1:33.283">a</span> <span begin="1:33.283" end="1:34.371">way</span> <span begin="1:34.371" end="1:35.140">a</span><span begin="1:35.140" end="1:35.948">head</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">前方必有出路可寻</span></p><p begin="1:36.196" end="1:39.951" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.196" end="1:36.604">Fire</span><span begin="1:36.604" end="1:37.114">works</span> <span begin="1:37.114" end="1:38.895">bloom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">烟花绽放</span></p><p begin="1:37.666" end="1:39.951" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:37.666" end="1:38.074">Just</span> <span begin="1:38.074" end="1:38.516">like</span> <span begin="1:38.516" end="1:38.932">a</span> <span begin="1:38.932" end="1:39.951">poem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宛如诗篇</span></p><p begin="1:39.951" end="1:43.604" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:39.951" end="1:40.854">Colorful</span> <span begin="1:40.854" end="1:41.273">yet</span> <span begin="1:41.273" end="1:43.400">brief</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">绚烂多姿却短暂</span></p><p begin="1:41.355" end="1:43.604" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:41.355" end="1:41.723">It</span> <span begin="1:41.723" end="1:42.077">doe</span><span begin="1:42.077" end="1:42.675">sn&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:42.675" end="1:43.604">matter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没关系</span></p><p begin="1:43.604" end="1:52.994" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:43.604" end="1:45.464">Every</span><span begin="1:45.464" end="1:46.430">thing</span> <span begin="1:46.430" end="1:46.845">you</span> <span begin="1:46.985" end="1:47.339">do</span> <span begin="1:47.339" end="1:48.085">for</span> <span begin="1:48.085" end="1:48.977">it</span> <span begin="1:49.261" end="1:51.008">will</span> <span begin="1:51.008" end="1:52.994">last</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你付出的一切努力，终会留存</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:43.604" end="1:52.994"><span begin="1:43.604" end="1:45.464">(Every</span><span begin="1:45.464" end="1:46.430">thing</span> <span begin="1:46.834" end="1:47.165">you</span> <span begin="1:47.165" end="1:48.015">do</span> <span begin="1:48.015" end="1:48.689">for</span> <span begin="1:48.689" end="1:49.135">it</span> <span begin="1:49.261" end="1:51.008">will</span> <span begin="1:51.008" end="1:52.994">last)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你付出的努力，终会留存</span></span></p><p begin="2:23.454" end="2:26.905" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.454" end="2:24.254">Every</span> <span begin="2:24.254" end="2:25.154">journey</span> <span begin="2:25.154" end="2:25.500">is</span> <span begin="2:25.500" end="2:26.454">unique</span> <span begin="2:26.454" end="2:26.905">just</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每段旅程都独一无二</span></p><p begin="2:26.905" end="2:30.619" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:26.905" end="2:27.390">Like</span> <span begin="2:27.390" end="2:27.886">the</span> <span begin="2:27.886" end="2:28.417">trails</span> <span begin="2:28.417" end="2:28.848">that</span> <span begin="2:28.848" end="2:29.263">fire</span><span begin="2:29.263" end="2:29.745">works</span> <span begin="2:29.745" end="2:30.199">leave</span> <span begin="2:30.199" end="2:30.619">and</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如同烟花划过的轨迹</span></p><p begin="2:30.619" end="2:34.348" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:30.619" end="2:31.126">Some</span> <span begin="2:31.126" end="2:31.582">will</span> <span begin="2:31.582" end="2:32.022">soar</span> <span begin="2:32.022" end="2:32.480">high,</span> <span begin="2:32.480" end="2:32.947">glow</span> <span begin="2:32.947" end="2:33.416">in</span> <span begin="2:33.416" end="2:33.875">the</span> <span begin="2:33.875" end="2:34.348">sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有的高飞，光芒闪烁</span></p><p begin="2:34.348" end="2:38.008" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:34.348" end="2:34.816">Some</span> <span begin="2:34.816" end="2:35.286">will</span> <span begin="2:35.286" end="2:35.731">wink</span> <span begin="2:35.731" end="2:36.203">out,</span> <span begin="2:36.203" end="2:36.662">sink</span> <span begin="2:36.662" end="2:37.115">in</span> <span begin="2:37.115" end="2:37.590">the</span> <span begin="2:37.590" end="2:38.008">sea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有的熄灭，沉入海底</span></p><p begin="2:38.008" end="2:41.716" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:38.008" end="2:38.512">I</span> <span begin="2:38.512" end="2:38.966">wish</span> <span begin="2:38.966" end="2:39.383">to</span> <span begin="2:39.383" end="2:39.859">shine</span> <span begin="2:39.859" end="2:40.846">brightly</span> <span begin="2:40.846" end="2:41.275">at</span> <span begin="2:41.275" end="2:41.716">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我愿夜空中璀璨闪耀</span></p><p begin="2:41.716" end="2:45.427" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.716" end="2:42.182">Yet</span> <span begin="2:42.182" end="2:42.645">fear</span> <span begin="2:42.645" end="2:43.611">being</span> <span begin="2:43.611" end="2:44.056">lost</span> <span begin="2:44.056" end="2:44.515">in</span> <span begin="2:44.515" end="2:44.974">the</span> <span begin="2:44.974" end="2:45.427">dark</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">却又惧怕迷失于黑暗</span></p><p begin="2:45.427" end="2:50.979" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.427" end="2:45.880">See</span> <span begin="2:45.880" end="2:46.314">the</span> <span begin="2:46.314" end="2:46.779">fire</span><span begin="2:46.779" end="2:47.262">works</span> <span begin="2:47.262" end="2:48.227">shining</span> <span begin="2:48.227" end="2:48.643">on</span> <span begin="2:48.643" end="2:49.075">this</span> <span begin="2:49.075" end="2:50.979">road</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你看那烟花照亮了前路</span></p><p begin="2:52.425" end="2:55.662" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:52.425" end="2:52.584">Flame</span> <span begin="2:52.584" end="2:52.811">of</span> <span begin="2:52.811" end="2:53.934">love</span> <span begin="2:54.118" end="2:54.291">flame</span> <span begin="2:54.291" end="2:54.534">of</span> <span begin="2:54.534" end="2:55.662">life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">爱的焰火，生命之光</span></p><p begin="2:55.859" end="3:00.226" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:55.859" end="2:56.014">The</span> <span begin="2:56.014" end="2:56.478">brightest</span> <span begin="2:56.478" end="2:58.442">moment</span> <span begin="2:58.442" end="2:59.075">I</span> <span begin="2:59.075" end="3:00.226">find</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是我见过最闪亮的时光</span></p><p begin="3:00.226" end="3:03.871" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:00.226" end="3:00.638">Fire</span><span begin="3:00.638" end="3:01.055">works</span> <span begin="3:01.055" end="3:03.314">bloom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">烟花绽放</span></p><p begin="3:01.594" end="3:03.871" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="3:01.594" end="3:02.005">Just</span> <span begin="3:02.005" end="3:02.468">like</span> <span begin="3:02.468" end="3:02.919">a</span> <span begin="3:02.919" end="3:03.871">poem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宛如诗篇</span></p><p begin="3:03.871" end="3:07.535" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:03.871" end="3:04.818">Colorful</span> <span begin="3:04.818" end="3:05.227">yet</span> <span begin="3:05.227" end="3:07.452">brief</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">绚烂多姿却短暂</span></p><p begin="3:05.288" end="3:07.535" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="3:05.288" end="3:05.715">It</span> <span begin="3:05.715" end="3:06.128">doe</span><span begin="3:06.128" end="3:06.616">sn&apos;t</span> <span begin="3:06.616" end="3:07.535">matter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没关系</span></p><p begin="3:07.535" end="3:16.891" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:07.535" end="3:09.485">Every</span><span begin="3:09.485" end="3:10.396">thing</span> <span begin="3:10.396" end="3:11.096">you</span> <span begin="3:11.096" end="3:11.262">do</span> <span begin="3:11.262" end="3:11.937">for</span> <span begin="3:11.937" end="3:12.693">it</span> <span begin="3:13.133" end="3:14.999">will</span> <span begin="3:14.999" end="3:16.891">last</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你付出的一切努力，终会留存</span></p><p begin="3:07.535" end="3:16.891" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="3:07.535" end="3:09.485">Every</span><span begin="3:09.485" end="3:10.396">thing</span> <span begin="3:10.828" end="3:11.279">you</span> <span begin="3:11.279" end="3:12.101">do</span> <span begin="3:12.101" end="3:12.677">for</span> <span begin="3:12.677" end="3:13.133">it</span> <span begin="3:13.133" end="3:14.999">will</span> <span begin="3:14.999" end="3:16.891">last</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你付出的努力，终会留存</span></p><p begin="3:17.394" end="3:19.878" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:17.394" end="3:17.662">Don&apos;t</span> <span begin="3:17.662" end="3:18.184">be</span> <span begin="3:18.184" end="3:19.878">afraid</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不用担心</span></p><p begin="3:33.395" end="3:35.834" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:33.395" end="3:33.651">Light</span> <span begin="3:33.651" end="3:33.907">up</span> <span begin="3:33.907" end="3:34.128">the</span> <span begin="3:34.128" end="3:34.848">night</span> <span begin="3:34.848" end="3:35.045">and</span> <span begin="3:35.045" end="3:35.834">shine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">点亮夜空，闪耀光辉</span></p><p begin="3:35.834" end="3:39.894" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:35.834" end="3:36.031">So</span> <span begin="3:36.031" end="3:36.955">dazzling</span> <span begin="3:36.955" end="3:37.139">as</span> <span begin="3:37.139" end="3:38.452">dreams</span> <span begin="3:38.452" end="3:38.725">and</span> <span begin="3:38.725" end="3:39.894">desires</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如梦似愿，光芒万丈</span></p><p begin="3:40.078" end="3:43.605" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:40.078" end="3:40.356">A</span> <span begin="3:40.356" end="3:40.628">warm</span> <span begin="3:40.628" end="3:40.905">and</span> <span begin="3:40.905" end="3:42.172">glowing</span> <span begin="3:42.172" end="3:43.605">light</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">温暖柔和的光辉</span></p><p begin="3:43.605" end="3:46.704" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:43.605" end="3:44.407">Filling</span> <span begin="3:44.407" end="3:44.635">the</span> <span begin="3:44.635" end="3:45.152">whole</span> <span begin="3:45.152" end="3:46.704">sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">照亮整片天空</span></p><p begin="3:48.244" end="3:50.519" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:48.244" end="3:48.423">The</span> <span begin="3:48.423" end="3:48.742">taste</span> <span begin="3:48.742" end="3:48.922">of</span> <span begin="3:48.922" end="3:49.602">home,</span> <span begin="3:49.602" end="3:49.789">how</span> <span begin="3:49.789" end="3:50.519">sweet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像家的气息，多么甜蜜</span></p><p begin="3:50.519" end="3:54.855" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:50.519" end="3:50.757">And</span> <span begin="3:50.757" end="3:51.402">bitter</span> <span begin="3:51.402" end="3:51.551">it</span> <span begin="3:51.551" end="3:51.847">can</span> <span begin="3:51.847" end="3:52.653">be</span> <span begin="3:52.653" end="3:53.286">some</span><span begin="3:53.286" end="3:54.855">times</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有时却又那么苦涩</span></p><p begin="3:54.855" end="4:01.586" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:54.855" end="3:55.493">Guiding</span> <span begin="3:55.493" end="3:55.639">my</span> <span begin="3:55.639" end="3:56.226">heart</span> <span begin="3:56.226" end="3:57.651">every</span> <span begin="3:57.651" end="3:58.327">step</span> <span begin="3:58.327" end="3:58.780">through</span> <span begin="3:58.780" end="3:59.271">the</span> <span begin="3:59.271" end="4:01.586">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">指引我心，步步前行穿过黑夜</span></p><p begin="4:02.523" end="4:05.918" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:02.523" end="4:02.687">Flame</span> <span begin="4:02.687" end="4:02.942">of</span> <span begin="4:02.942" end="4:04.127">love,</span> <span begin="4:04.127" end="4:04.359">flame</span> <span begin="4:04.359" end="4:04.543">of</span> <span begin="4:04.543" end="4:05.918">life,</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">爱的焰火，生命之光</span></p><p begin="4:05.918" end="4:10.361" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:05.918" end="4:06.135">The</span> <span begin="4:06.135" end="4:06.687">brightest</span> <span begin="4:06.687" end="4:08.458">moment</span> <span begin="4:08.458" end="4:09.170">I</span> <span begin="4:09.170" end="4:10.361">find</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是我见过最闪亮的时光</span></p><p begin="4:10.361" end="4:13.618" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:10.361" end="4:11.039">I</span> <span begin="4:11.039" end="4:11.794">am</span> <span begin="4:11.794" end="4:13.618">convinced</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我确信</span></p><p begin="4:13.618" end="4:17.302" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:13.618" end="4:13.807">It&apos;s</span> <span begin="4:13.807" end="4:14.053">a</span> <span begin="4:14.053" end="4:14.685">new</span> <span begin="4:14.685" end="4:15.480">start</span> <span begin="4:15.480" end="4:15.682">of</span> <span begin="4:15.682" end="4:15.916">grand</span> <span begin="4:15.916" end="4:17.302">dreams</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这便是盛大梦想的开场</span></p><p begin="4:17.302" end="4:20.384" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:17.302" end="4:17.453">Just</span> <span begin="4:17.453" end="4:17.715">keep</span> <span begin="4:17.715" end="4:18.986">going,</span> <span begin="4:18.986" end="4:19.184">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="4:19.184" end="4:19.371">look</span> <span begin="4:19.371" end="4:20.384">back</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">继续前行，莫回首</span></p><p begin="4:20.803" end="4:24.925" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:20.803" end="4:21.041">There</span> <span begin="4:21.041" end="4:21.187">must</span> <span begin="4:21.187" end="4:21.472">be</span> <span begin="4:21.472" end="4:22.197">a</span> <span begin="4:22.197" end="4:23.299">way</span> <span begin="4:23.299" end="4:23.993">a</span><span begin="4:23.993" end="4:24.925">head</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">前方必定有路可寻</span></p><p begin="4:25.168" end="4:28.821" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:25.168" end="4:25.557">Fire</span><span begin="4:25.557" end="4:25.966">works</span> <span begin="4:25.966" end="4:27.925">bloom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">烟花绽放</span></p><p begin="4:26.501" end="4:28.821" itunes:key="L56" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="4:26.501" end="4:26.971">Just</span> <span begin="4:26.971" end="4:27.400">like</span> <span begin="4:27.400" end="4:27.834">a</span> <span begin="4:27.834" end="4:28.821">poem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宛如诗篇</span></p><p begin="4:28.821" end="4:32.506" itunes:key="L57" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:28.821" end="4:29.752">Colorful</span> <span begin="4:29.752" end="4:30.133">yet</span> <span begin="4:30.133" end="4:32.184">brief</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">绚烂多姿却短暂</span></p><p begin="4:30.202" end="4:32.506" itunes:key="L58" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="4:30.202" end="4:30.617">It</span> <span begin="4:30.617" end="4:31.025">doe</span><span begin="4:31.025" end="4:31.570">sn&apos;t</span> <span begin="4:31.570" end="4:32.506">matter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没关系</span></p><p begin="4:32.506" end="4:41.903" itunes:key="L59" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:32.506" end="4:34.341">Every</span><span begin="4:34.341" end="4:35.384">thing</span> <span begin="4:35.384" end="4:35.766">you</span> <span begin="4:35.766" end="4:36.308">do</span> <span begin="4:36.308" end="4:36.957">for</span> <span begin="4:36.957" end="4:37.716">it</span> <span begin="4:38.093" end="4:39.943">will</span> <span begin="4:39.943" end="4:41.903">last</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你付出的一切努力，终会留存</span></p><p begin="4:32.506" end="4:41.903" itunes:key="L60" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="4:32.506" end="4:34.341">Every</span><span begin="4:34.341" end="4:35.384">thing</span> <span begin="4:35.797" end="4:36.215">you</span> <span begin="4:36.215" end="4:36.943">do</span> <span begin="4:36.943" end="4:37.495">for</span> <span begin="4:37.495" end="4:38.076">it</span> <span begin="4:38.093" end="4:39.943">will</span> <span begin="4:39.943" end="4:41.903">last</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你付出的一切努力，终会留存</span></p><p begin="4:42.235" end="4:45.538" itunes:key="L61" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:42.235" end="4:42.703">Just</span> <span begin="4:42.703" end="4:43.173">go</span> <span begin="4:43.173" end="4:43.463">a</span><span begin="4:43.463" end="4:45.538">head</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只管去做</span></p></div></body></tt>